+## Image Search Proxy Dev Fallback
+
+- Created rollback archive:
+  `Docs/Design/FolderEditorArchive/2026-05-04-before-image-proxy-dev-fallback/`.
+- Made the local image-search proxy usable for simulator folder-cover QA even
+  when `PEXELS_API_KEY` is not configured.
+- Added a `SAVI Demo` fallback provider that returns deterministic development
+  image results and lets `/image-download` convert selected demo images into
+  normal JPEG data URLs for the app.
+- Kept production behavior explicit: set `SAVI_IMAGE_PROXY_DEMO_FALLBACK=0` to
+  disable demo images and require a real Pexels API key.
+- Updated proxy setup docs to explain local simulator usage with
+  `SAVI_IMAGE_SEARCH_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787`.
+- Verified `/health`, `/image-search`, and `/image-download`; launched
+  `SAVI Test` with the local proxy URL so the Folder editor can enable
+  `Find image` during simulator QA.
